# Backend Models & Domain

## Models

### User (`models/User.js`)
- `name`, `email` (unique, lowercase), `password` (bcrypt, `select: false`, min 6)
- `plan`: `'credit'` only
- `usedMinutes`, `usedSeconds`, `usedAiNotes`
- `audioSecondsBalance` default 3600, `aiNotesBalance` default 10
- `usagePeriodStart`, timestamps
- `comparePassword(candidate)`

### Admin (`models/Admin.js`)
- User와 동일 password 패턴, 별도 collection
- register/login 시 Admin 이메일이면 일반 auth 403

### Upload (`models/Upload.js`)
- `user` (ref User), `originalName`, `cloudinaryUrl`, `publicId`
- `duration`, `format`, `bytes`, `status`: `uploaded | failed`

### Transcript (`models/Transcript.js`)
- `upload` (ref, **unique**), `user`, `status`, `content` (Mixed), `error`
- `billedSeconds` — 차감 완료 시 기록

### Memo (`models/Memo.js`)
- `user`, `upload` (**unique**), `transcript`, `title`, `preview`
- `words`, `segments` (Mixed arrays, nullable)

### Payment (`models/Payment.js`)
- `user`, `paymentId` (unique), `packId`, `creditAudioSeconds`, `creditAiNotes`
- `orderName`, `amount`, `currency` default KRW
- `status`: `pending | paid | failed | cancelled`
- `paymentType`: `credit_pack`, `portoneStatus`, `paidAt`

